<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Luipi gal lam mun hawih nuomtak akhun,
 Mi sang zatam tuibang kigawm diel!
 Van ah Hukdampa lungsiet, thutak a dim,
 Tawh tanbang kikim thei kuo a um?

[V2]
 Aw, A lienpen ie sang-zatam lai ah,
 A pahchakna tuibang luong zel hen;
 &quot;Amah bangkim bangkim ah A hawihpen hi&quot;
 I kumsawt zaila diu chu hi hen.

[V3]
 2. Amah bangkim, bangkim ah A hawihpen hi,
 Nem dildiel in A hun sam zing hi;
 A hukdamna athawn-aval a piek hih,
 Ka thagau, bangdi'n pawmlo ding maw?

[V4]
 3. Amah bangkim, bangkim ah A hawihpen hi,
 A aw ngai un, A hun sam zing hi;
 &quot;Hung un! hung un! lungkham leh puokgik pawte,
 Ka kawm ah na puokgik uh hung ngau!&quot;</lyrics>
<title>ALTOGETHER LOVELY</title>
<hymn_number>34</hymn_number>
</song>